# Copy this file to Makefile.local and fill in your Developer ID identity.
# Makefile.local is gitignored.
#
# Find your identity with:  security find-identity -v -p codesigning
#
# DEVELOPER_ID := Developer ID Application: Your Name (TEAMID)

# ---- v0.2 Session Workspace smoke checklist ----
# 1. ⌘⇧N quick capture flow still works end-to-end (regression check).
# 2. Library still loads existing Nudge-* folders unchanged.
# 3. Menu bar → "Open Session Workspace…" opens the new window.
# 4. First time: agent config editor appears; add an agent, save.
# 5. New session dialog accepts cwd + agent + name; Create spawns terminal.
# 6. zsh prompt visible in chosen cwd; pwd, ls work.
# 7. ⌘N creates a second tab on a different cwd; switching tabs swaps the terminal.
# 8. ⌘\ collapses and restores the render pane.
# 9. Close tab → library shows it with LOOP badge → Resume re-spawns the pty in same cwd.
# 10. Quit app → relaunch → library still shows the loop session.
